      <title>毗湿奴之子卡玛：爱神被焚与重生的神话</title>
      <link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/india/%E5%8D%A1%E7%8E%9B%E7%88%B1%E7%A5%9E/</link>
